kanga pirau
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:fermented corn
Origin: Maori
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: first word also spelt kaanga; second word also piro, kopiro, kopirau; also kanga wai kopiro
